A 3D variational autoencoder that compresses videos spatially and temporally, improving compression rate and video accuracy.an expert transformer block to help align text and video, and a 3D full attention module for capturing and creating spatially and temporally accurate videos.

name: Davant
description:
Davant Studio is the easiest way to supercharge your next creative project with AI image generation. Available for PC and Mac, it’s 100% offline so you’re in control of the resources you use and the images you create.

The one-click installer makes setting up Stable Diffusion painless: Davant provides “ready to go” bundles for different platforms. Your hardware is detected, and the compatible version is automatically selected.

Davant Studio has been purpose-built for working professionals and creators. The streamlined interface puts the important controls at your fingertips for maximum flexibility and control, and the real-time generation engine unlocks new ways to experiment and explore. Get ready for imagination without limits.
